    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "SceneKit draws a shadow map image by rendering the scene from the point of view of the node containing the light. Directional lights ignore the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnnode/1408026-position"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property of the node containing them because their light has a constant direction. Therefore, rendering a shadow map for a directional light requires an orthographic projection. Like the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scncamera/1436612-orthographicscale"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property of a camera object, this property specifies the extent of the scene “visible to” the light when rendering the shadow map."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This property applies only if the light’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnlight/1522919-type"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnlighttypedirectional"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
